Inside the cave, through a tunnel and past a cage a firefight was
going on. RODIMUS PRIMAL was holding a battle with several figures in
strange armored suits and carrying laser rifles. At the same time he
was slowly backing up towards a tunnel behind him.

Meanwhile inside the tunnel PERCEPTOR was dragging a similarly
outfitted figure as RODIMUS was fighting, but this one was
unconscious.

WINDLORD and RAT TRAP were entering the same tunnel, laser fire and
the stink of burning metal and debris in the air from the fire fight
ahead.

About center of the tunnel PERCEPTOR, WINDLORD and RAT TRAP meet, each
going in the other direction, two going to help RODIMUS and the last
trying to get out.

"Are you through yet?" Came a fierce whisper to PERCEPTOR across the
comlinks. It would seem that communications worked -inside- the cave,
they just could not penetrate outside of it to reach the ark.

Perhaps it was the minerals and such lining the rock.

(TAG)

- Preston
